title: 292. Andy & DJ CTI: No Charges For Mike Tyson, House Approves $40B For Ukraine & Jack Dorsey Wishes He Hadn’t Banned Trump
itunes:title: 292. Andy & DJ CTI: No Charges For Mike Tyson, House Approves $40B For Ukraine & Jack Dorsey Wishes He Hadn’t Banned Trump
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ discuss the California district attorney's decision to not file charges against Mike Tyson after a physical altercation with another passenger on a JetBlue flight, the House sending an additional $40 Billion to aid Ukraine in the conflict with Russia, and Jack Dorsey agreeing that former President Donald Trump shouldn't have been banned from Twitter.
